From the Infowars web site :: On the Tuesday, July 2 edition of The Alex Jones Show, Alex breaks down how the United Nations has long had a plan in place for a general and complete disarmament of United States citizens and to ultimately integrate a progressively strengthened U.N. Peace force. 

Alex also reviews the accelerating disintegration of Posse Comitatus as Americans are acclimated to accept Russian forces to provide "security at mass events." 

We'll also cover how riots may be on the horizon if George Zimmerman is acquitted of the murder of Trayvon Martin. 

On today's show, Alex welcomes in studio guest NASA Mission Operations Control Room flight control monitor Raymond Teague who worked on the Apollo program. 

Public Enemy's Professor Griff, the Minister of Information, is also in studio to discuss the Illuminati takeover of hip hop and to conduct a special Ask Alex segment.
